<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨٩٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a>: عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«هَذِهِ وَهَذِهِ سَوَاءٌ»</span>. يَعْنِي الْخِنْصَرَ وَالْإِبْهَامَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>